This file documents the revision history for Perl extension Text::Markdown.

        - Fixed bug preventing single quotes from being used to delimit
            link titles
        - Fixed bug where </code> is rendered in the wrong place when an escaped
            backtick is in the code block
        - Fixed bug where \`notcode\` was still being put in code blocks
        - Added markdown output tests based on
            http://daringfireball.net/projects/markdown/ documentation

1.03  2005-11-09 00:00:00
        - Added support for options to non-oo api

1.02  2005-11-09 00:00:00
        - Added option handling

1.01  2005-10-24 00:00:00
        - first release
